      <title>美国商会：香港在美国的不良形象意味着政策不会转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/hong-kong-s-poor-image-in-us-means-no-policy-shift-amcham</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港美国商会在访问美国首都后表示，香港在华盛顿的声誉太差，难以指望有任何政策压力的缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/hong-kong-s-poor-image-in-us-means-no-policy-shift-amcham</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:05:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡要求 Facebook 和 X 屏蔽中国富豪郭文贵的帖子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/singapore-orders-facebook-x-to-block-chinese-tycoon-guo-s-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡指示社交媒体平台封锁流亡中国大亨郭文贵的近 100 个网络账号，原因是其帖子被认为损害了该城国的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/singapore-orders-facebook-x-to-block-chinese-tycoon-guo-s-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:39:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国互联网瘫痪，抗议活动不断扩大，已造成 25 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/bangladesh-internet-goes-dark-as-widening-job-protests-kill-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国全国范围内的互联网中断，因为手持棍棒和石块的学生与警方发生冲突，抗议政府，据报道，此次冲突已造成至少 25 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/bangladesh-internet-goes-dark-as-widening-job-protests-kill-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
